pull_request.title: CMakeLists: add ppc case to known archs
pull_request.body:
This is a trivial PR: it simply adds `ppc` to a list of known archs, retaining a warning re no CI for this platform.

I have confirmed the build on Darwin ppc for `liboqs` 0.10.1 with no other alterations to the code.

pull_request.body:
Signed-off-by: Duc Tri Nguyen <dnguye69@gmu.edu>

<!-- Please give a brief explanation of the purpose of this pull request. -->

- Add additional XMSS parameters to meet NIST SP 800 208. 
- Add emoji to Table parameters `sig_stfl_xmss.h`, I hope it's helpful and save developer time. 
- Add KATs. 
- Add tests.
